<body>
<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="objectType">Wall</rs> of  doorway to stage room.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on a rough surface. To the left, the letters have been worn or rubbed away, and a hole has been cut into l.2.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Irregular, lunate, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.04-0.07</measure>; perhaps two hands. There are traces of red paint in some letters.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p><date notBefore="0001" notAfter="0600">First  to sixth century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">context</rs>)</p>
</div>
<div type="edition" lang="grc">
<head lang="en">Edition</head>
<ab>
<lb n="1"/>
<persName type="aphrodisian"><name reg="Παρδαλᾶς">Π<unclear reason="damage">αρδα</unclear>λᾶ</name></persName> <w lemma="μιμόλογος">μειμολόγου</w> 
<lb n="2"/>
<persName type="aphrodisian"><name reg="Σύρος"><unclear reason="damage">Συρ</unclear>ου</name></persName> <w lemma="σκεῦος">σ<unclear reason="damage">κε</unclear>ύ<unclear reason="damage">η</unclear></w>
<w lemma="μετά">μ<unclear reason="damage">ετ</unclear>ὰ</w> <persName type="aphrodisian"><name reg="Φιλιστίων">Φιλιστίων<unclear reason="damage">α</unclear></name></persName></ab>
</div>

<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>Of Pardalas, mime. Equipment of Syrus, after Philistion</p>
<p>or </p><p>Equipment of Pardalas, Syrian mime, after Philistion</p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>One of the group of inscriptions, apparently by performers, at the doorways of the rooms on the stage front:  <xref type="inscription" n="698" href="080008">8.8</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="700" href="080104">8.104</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1567" href="080015">8.15</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1707" href="080016">8.16</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1716" href="080017">8.17</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1754" href="080018">8.18</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1755" href="080019">8.19</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1759" href="080020">8.20</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1760" href="080021">8.21</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="1895" href="080022">8.22</xref>. See <bibl n="PPA">Roueché, <title>PPA</title>, pp. 15-25.</bibl></p>
</div>
